    <div class="mid">
      <h2>Info</h2>
      <p>Left to Die is a platformer inspired by traditional Mario and by some of its quirky spin-offs, namely <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Shobon_Action">Syobon Action</a> (AKA Cat Mario), <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/I_Wanna_Be_the_Guy">I Wanna Be the Guy</a>, and <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/VVVVVV">VVVVVV</a>. It was made as part of <a href="http://vgdc-uci.com/">VGDC UCI</a>'s 2015 winter quarter weekend game jam. The theme was 'Choose a Side', and we decided to put our own spin on the platformer genre, where facing left inverses all the blocks the character interacts with.</p>

      <ul>
	<li>Made by: Max Chung, Kinsey Lynaugh, Hector Martinez, Andrew Chau</li>
	<li>Download: <a href="LeftToDie.zip" download>LeftToDie.zip</a> (7.1 MB)</li>
	<li>Repository: <a href="https://github.com/shrackner/lefttodie">lefttodie</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

